data.meta_description: That’s exactly what Gush Etzion is: home.A place that combines Tanach, #history, #culture, breathtaking #views, and #people of all kinds. It’s this unique atmosphere which motivated me to set into motion two innovative projects that have struck roots in Gush Etzion
